## Overview

The JSON format consists of:
- **Presentation metadata**
- **Slides array** with layout specifications and content
- **Inline formatting** using markdown-style syntax
- **Mixed content support** (text + visualizations in same layout)
- **Column/position-based** content organization
- **Custom fit layouts** for exact template control (NEW!)

