}
```

### 2. Add Slides Using Exact Layouts

Each slide needs a layout and content. Use exact layout names for precise control:

#### Title Slide
```json
{
  "layout": {
    "type": "exact",
    "name": "1_Title Slide"
  },
  "content": {
    "title": "**Q4 2024 Business Review**",
    "subtitle": "Performance, Insights, and Strategic Direction"
